cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DB

The paper deals with automated methods for classifying textual documents, which is a common problem in information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The proposed methods involve machine learning algorithms (cs.LG) and semantic analysis (cs.AI), which are also relevant sub-categories. Finally, the paper focuses on the biomedical domain, which involves handling large amounts of data and requires efficient database management (cs.DB).
